            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4800,
            "LocalizeKR": "자아,\n제 옆에 앉아주세요.\n선생님.",
            "LocalizeJP": "ほら、先生？\nこっちに来てください。",
